    Structure that is being used to store the results from SPSM and matches. Represents one match between a source schema and a target schema, with its similarity score and the repaired schema and the SPARQL query that is generated from the repaired schema This structure will have a similarity value, the name of the target, a list of the individual matches and relations as well as storing how many individual matches this target has
